'Winner (4):''' [[1934 FIFA World Cup|1934]], [[1938 FIFA World Cup|1938]], [[1982 FIFA World Cup|1982]], [[2006 FIFA World Cup|2006]]\n:* Runner-up (2): [[1970 FIFA World Cup|1970]], [[1994 FIFA World Cup|1994]]\n:* Third place (1): [[1990 FIFA World Cup|1990]]\n:* Fourth place (1): [[1978 FIFA World Cup|1978]]\n* '''[[UEFA European Championship]]'''\n:* '''Winner (1):''' [[UEFA Euro 1968|1968]]\n:* Runner-up (2): [[UEFA Euro 2000|2000]], [[UEFA Euro 2012|2012]]\n:* Fourth place (1): [[UEFA Euro 1980|1980]]\n:* Semi-finals (1): [[UEFA Euro 1988|1988]]\n* '''[[FIFA Confederations Cup]]'''\n:* Third place (1): [[2013 FIFA Confederations Cup|2013]]\n* '''[[Football at the Summer Olympics|Olympic football tournament]]'''\n:* '''Gold Medal (1):''' [[Football at the 1936 Summer Olympics|1936]]\n:* Bronze Medal (2): [[Football at the 1928 Summer Olympics|1928]], [[Football at the 2004 Summer Olympics&nbsp;\u2013 Men's tournament|2004]]\n'''Minor titles''':\n* '''[[Central European International Cup]]'''\n:* '''Winner (2):''' [[1927\u201330 Central European International Cup|1927\u201330]], [[1933\u201335 Central European International Cup|1933\u201335]]\n:* Runner-up (2): [[1931\u201332 Central European International Cup|1931\u201332]], [[1936\u201338 Central European International Cup|1936\u201338]]{{#tag:ref|This edition of the tournament was interrupted due to the annexation of Austria to Nazi Germany on 12 March 1938.|name=\"ceic\"|group=\"nb\"}}\n{{Col-2}}\n\n===Awards===\n* '''[[Laureus World Sports Award for Team of the Year|Laureus World Team of the Year]]'''\n:* '''Winners:''' 2007\n{{col-end}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=30% style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Competition !!{{gold1}} !!{{silver2}} !!{{bronze3}} !!Total\n|-\n|align=left|[[FIFA World Cup|World Cup]]\n|4 || 2 || 1 || 7\n|-\n|align=left|[[UEFA European Championship|European Championship]]\n|1 || 2 || 0 || 3\n|-\n|align=left|[[FIFA Confederations Cup|Confederations Cup]]\n|0 || 0 || 1