l Pro Auto Parts 500|CLT]]<br />{{small|33}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[1989 Holly Farms 400|NWS]]<br />{{small|8}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[AC Delco 500|CAR]]<br />{{small|16}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1989 Autoworks 500|PHO]]<br />{{small|33}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[1989 Atlanta Journal 500|ATL]]<br />{{small|11}}\n| colspan=5|\n! 22nd\n! 2919\n! <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/irvaner01/1989/W|title=Ernie Irvan \u2013 1989 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=October 2, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=3| [[1990 NASCAR Winston Cup Series|1990]]\n! [[Donlavey Racing]]\n! 90\n! [[Ford Motor Company|Ford]]\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[1990 Daytona 500|DAY]]<br />{{small|13}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Pontiac Excitement 400|RCH]]<br />{{small|22}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[GM Goodwrench 500|CAR]]<br />{{small|29}}\n| colspan=31|\n! rowspan=3| 9th\n! rowspan=3| 3593\t\n! rowspan=3| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/irvaner01/1990/W|title=Ernie Irvan \u2013 1990 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=October 2, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=5| [[Morgan-McClure Motorsports]]\n! rowspan=5| 4\n! [[Oldsmobile|Olds]]\n| colspan=3|\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Motorcraft Quality Parts 500|ATL]]<br />{{small|3}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[TranSouth 500|DAR]]<br />{{small|32}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| '''[[Valleydale Meats 500|BRI]]'''<br />{{small|16}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[First Union 400|NWS]]<br />{{small|16}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Hanes Activewear 500|MAR]]<br />{{small|15}}\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Winston 500 (Spring)|TAL]]<br />{{small|4}}\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Coca-Cola 600|CLT]]<br />{{small|5}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Budweiser 500 (Spring Dover)|DOV]]<br />{{small|7}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Banquet Froz