et/irvaner01/1998/W|title=Ernie Irvan \u2013 1998 NASCAR Winston Cup Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=October 2, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[1999 NASCAR Winston Cup Series|1999]]\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[1999 Daytona 500|DAY]]<br />{{small|14}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Dura Lube/Big K 400|CAR]]<br />{{small|29}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Las Vegas 400|LVS]]<br />{{small|6}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Cracker Barrel 500|ATL]]<br />{{small|7}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[1999 TranSouth Financial 400|DAR]]<br />{{small|24}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Primestar 500 (Texas)|TEX]]<br />{{small|37}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Food City 500|BRI]]<br /><small>43</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Goody's Body Pain 500|MAR]]<br />{{small|22}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[DieHard 500 (Spring Talladega)|TAL]]<br />{{small|40}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[California 500 Presented by NAPA|CAL]]<br />{{small|35}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Pontiac Excitement 400|RCH]]<br />{{small|33}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Coca-Cola 600|CLT]]<br />{{small|36}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[MBNA Platinum 400|DOV]]<br />{{small|35}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Kmart 400|MCH]]<br />{{small|7}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Pocono 500|POC]]<br />{{small|8}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Save Mart/Kragen 350|SON]]<br />{{small|30}}\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[1999 Pepsi 400|DAY]]<br />{{small|9}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Jiffy Lube 300|NHA]]<br />{{small|21}}\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Pennsylvania 500|POC]]<br />{{small|11}}\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Brickyard 400|IND]]<br />{{small|24}}\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1999 Frontier @ the Glen|GLN]]<br />{{small|41}}\n| [[Pepsi 400 Presented by Meijer|MCH]]\n| [[1999 Goody's Headache Powder 500|BRI]]\n| [[Pepsi Southern 500|DAR]]\n| [[Exide NASCAR Select Batteries 400|R